        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You've learned to make good use of your diminutive stature and angle your attacks when fighting larger enemies. If you critically hit a Large or larger enemy with a ranged Strike while using a weapon that fires projectile ammo, you knock them @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Prone]. A creature knocked prone by your unusually angled shots learns how to brace for impact, becoming immune to The Bigger They Are for 24 hours.</p>"
